          When you outgrow your own meeting: publish your operating system, learn from every other organization on the network, and run it all behind your own walls.
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-[var(--line)] pt-6 flex-1">
          <p class="font-mono text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[var(--blue-deep)] mb-4">Everything in Free, plus:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <% var paidFeatures = [
