        ['What exactly do I get for free?', 'Your org chart with unlimited human and AI seats, Radar your AI Chief of Staff, the full meeting (agenda, scorecard, rocks, issues, to-dos), and the SOPs your team writes for the agents to inherit. The complete meeting product, no credit card.'],
